{
  "stem": "26609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Erb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I put down that [INAUDIBLE] my sister's name later was from Spiegler changed to Erb.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as she came back, she got her [? part, ?] a big flat, furniture-- beautiful flat and furniture on [INAUDIBLE] in Lwow, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she got pregnant, though my mother wanted her to stay and have the child in Poland where she lived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a beautiful place there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And wait until-- so she had to wait nearly a year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the child was very young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she waited again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were not-- not in a hurry to return to Israel because they could return any time later on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was before independence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But since they were citizens of Israel-- they had documents-- they stayed so long until the boy was five years old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They lived a very comfortable life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there in my brother-in-law's-- his brother got a wife too with no children, got another flat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a huge place with a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The restaurant was left to his mother and some younger children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the three elder children were-- got flats.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know what they did there, their professions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And finally, '39 started the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were trapped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They couldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my-- I think I mentioned to you that my brother-in-law, my sister's husband, he studied once, how do you call, languages.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He knew a number of languages, including Italian and others-- Greek and other languages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He knew quite a lot of languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When the Germans came, the Italians-- Mussolini, you know, went together with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
